reviews.review_text:
Need the crowd ambiance to understand the show Odd show, just read the reviews on other forks.  Police, heat, rain, power, crowds, etc.

By the way - what genius thought that fencing off an acre of beautiful, fresh, green grass comprising the best seats in the stadium was a good idea?

The crowd and the weather contributed to this show more than was usual.  Hearing an isolated soundboard recording doesn't reflect the energy of the crowd, the lightning, the thunder, the heat, etc.

Nothing special about the soundboard audio, but the energy of everything else made this show memorable.
